Current Status

The Dynatrace workflow design is in progress for automating decommission DTSK backup validation.
The DTSK search output is available from ServiceNow, and the Cohesity JavaScript logic has been prepared to validate CI backup evidence, protection group, latest backup date, assignment status, SLA status, and multiple-cluster matches caused by replication.

Next Steps

Update the Dynatrace workflow with the latest Cohesity JS script.
Validate the script using one DTSK with a known CI backup in Cohesity.
Confirm the email output format, summary counts, SLA status, and legend.
Test the no-DTSK scenario to confirm the email still reports no active DTSKs.
Schedule the workflow to run every 6 hours after successful validation.
